The most advanced MVC framework for building HTML5 based web and mobile applications

Faug stands for generic automated UI framework

Model - Object oriented Schema Json
View - HTML Template
Controller - Js functions
Router - Configuration (config.json)
i18n - globalize/i18next
Dialogs - bootbox
Responsive - bootstrap
Utility library - jquery

Forms are auto-generated with the help of the defined schema specification
Crud operations or API's are also defined within a schema json to map read/add/update/fetch ajax call mappings
Completely heirarchial forms can be specified, easy to define/use validation checkpoints
Callbacks provide hooks to control the application workflow
